Application: Cascade Bare References Rejected
  Description: Bare "references X" with no cascade clause must fail (TERMIN-S codes a)
Id: a1c0c1a0-cade-4a00-9000-000000000010

Identity:
  Scopes are "bare.view", "bare.manage"
  A "tester" has "bare.view" and "bare.manage"

Content called "parents":
  Each parent has a name which is text, required
  Anyone with "bare.view" can view parents
  Anyone with "bare.manage" can create parents

Content called "children":
  Each child has a label which is text, required
  Each child has a parent which references parents, required
  Anyone with "bare.view" can view children
  Anyone with "bare.manage" can create children
